name: S3 Config
content:
aws.s3 {
      region = "ap-southeast-1"
      bucket = "ambience-cloud-demo"
      path = "[s3 folder path as xxx/xx]"
      accessId = "[aws_access_key_id]"
      secret = "[aws_secret_access_key encrypted]" 
      roleArn="arn:aws:iam::[aws account id]:role/[iam role allow s3 access]"
      roleSessionName ="ambience-s3-session"
      stsServiceEndpoint = "https://sts.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com"
      
}
